title: Nemesis draft game missing from match history?
body: My match history goes from an ARAM match to another ARAM match, even though I played a game of nemesis draft in between. Is this normal?

replies.body: I looked up your profile in the client, and guess it's not the account you're posting from.  It may take a bit for your match history to update, and I believe the website history is strict on ranked games.  Give it some time and it should be up!
Ummm. Well, I changed my summoner name from annekami > kami banani, if that helps? I still log in with the former. EDIT: There's the blitz game. Sorry about that!
